: 147}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待良子 26 年的体检报告，他的血糖血压甚至更健康了吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日，良子完成年度常规健康体检复查，对比历年体检数据可见，其血压、血糖两项核心慢病相关指标较往年管控效果更佳，数值趋于理想区间，身体基础健康水平实现明显提升，长期健康养护收获实质性成效。 良子今年的血糖和血压甚至更健康了 _ 娱乐频道 _ 中华网良子体检报告出来了！部分数据比上班族还健康 _ 游民星空 GamerSky.com"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-1bc843d77e3f76428262ef46aa6add9c_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "119 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2058494548238496671"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI6sHDgYXj3JsdEAMaCTEyMDM3MjkzMCDRiLzSBjAAOIsEQA1yEzIwNTg0OTQ1NDgyMzg0OTY2NzF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1783653603.394912", "card_id": "Q_2056885430310659867", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 52}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "张雪透露负债近 1 亿，称「这次卖了一点股份，本月就会还清，再也不欠钱了」，哪些信息值得关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "7 月 4 日，「张雪机车」品牌创始人张雪发布视频透露自己目前负债接近 1 亿元，这次卖了一点股份，本月就会把债务全部还清，「再也不欠钱了」。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-d3a60a962d56a06345ca5794ba854203_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "116 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2056885430310659867"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI6sHDgYXj3JsdEAMaCTEyMDMwMTI0MSC106TSBjAAOMUBQA5yEzIwNTY4ODU0MzAzMTA2NTk4Njd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "15_1783653603.395535", "card_id": "Q_2058579564071056764", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 48}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么总有人说真正的见世面「是去生产端，而非消费端」？这句话到底有没有道理？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "逛网红商圈打卡探店，探店下午茶、旅行打卡拍照、追逐各类奢侈品，见识各式各样的娱乐消遣方式。长期浸泡在消费端，只能学会怎样花钱享受生活，却很难看懂社会真实的运转逻辑。 \t 经济学里有一条基础概念：消费只能消耗资源，生产才可以创造价值。我们日常刷到的精致生活，本质上都是别人包装好的成品，属于消费环节。你只是作为接收者去体验别人打造好的结果。看得再多，只能学会享受生活方式，却摸不透背后的规则。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-03fd9bd0a26a524ce4b0f2e5ee312872_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "102 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2058579564071056764"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI6sHDgYXj3JsdEAMaCTEyMDM4MDExNyD+pr3SBjAAOLIBQA9yEzIwNTg1Nzk1NjQwNzEwNTY3NjR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_1783653603.396214", "card_id": "Q_589084113", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 49}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么现在大街上几乎看不到多少人穿高跟鞋了？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-391ad6a3bb8be4881da4c964fee75137_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "92 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/589084113"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I6sHDgYXj3JsdEAMaCDkzMTg5MjQ3IMjKtaAGMAA4UkAQcgk1ODkwODQxMTN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1783653603.396510", "card_id": "Q_2058507973886997487", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 333}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "雷军提出车内空间不该固定，小米澎程主打「空间自定义」，这有必要吗？会不会重新定义未来家用车的设计逻辑？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "7 月 9 日，雷军发文表示：今天，我们正式公布小米汽车的第二个产品系列：SkyNomad 小米澎程。 SU7/YU7 系列，是「驾驶者之车」；小米澎程系列，是「智能可变大空间 SUV」。这是小米造车 5 年多来，面向不同的用户需求，交出的两份不同的答卷。 针对为什么要做小米澎程？雷军表示：近几年，中国汽车工业取得了跨越式成就，「冰箱彩电大沙发」、「大六座大七座」已是寻常配置，市场供给相当足够。 但我们也看到，越来越多车主在选车的时候，不仅仅关心空间够不够大、座椅够不够舒服，更在意的是，呆在车里，是否自在。 他们每天通勤 2 小时，偶尔在车里午休小憩，有时在车上处理工作，周末带家人短途出游，露营时希望车就是第二个家。对他们来说，车不只是行驶载具，更是移动的「第 N 空间」。 怎样让一辆车真正令人自在？这是小米澎程在 2023 年初规划立项时，我们反复追问自己的核心命题。我们给出的答案是，用智能定义空间，打造一个「活的空间」。车内的空间不应该是固定的，应该可以随着你的需求和心意而自如变化。雷军官宣！小米汽车全新品牌，小米澎程来了 _ 大河财立方"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-550d350e044036182e1c9fccf6366867_r.jpg?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "92 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2058507973886997487"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI6sHDgYXj3JsdEAMaCTEyMDM3Mzk3MSDSobzSBjAAOIwEQBFyEzIwNTg1MDc5NzM4ODY5OTc0ODd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "18_1783653603.397380", "card_id": "Q_2058590759343896113", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 20}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "关于詹姆斯去向，杰佛森说已经定了要保密，富保罗说确实没定不想吊胃口，如何评价二人矛盾言论？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "[2 张图片]"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-75dda45208a4106676e98b382845c70d_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "87 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2058590759343896113"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI6sHDgYXj3JsdEAMaCTEyMDM4MTExNSDru73SBjAAOBNAEnITMjA1ODU5MDc1OTM0Mzg5NjExM3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1783653603.397795", "card_id": "Q_2057517515299878611", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 17}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《小学生社交情商漫画》等成为畅销童书，童书榜为何被「鸡汤、速成」书淹没？「伪童书」对孩子会有哪些影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "眼下，童书市场正被「伪童书」霸占。 新京报记者发现，在算法推荐机制下，大量带有功利倾向和成人化倾向的「伪童书」正借助平台投流和超低折扣的方式，系统性地占据童书销售榜单。与此同时，真正具有文学价值的优质儿童读物，却逐渐丧失触达读者的渠道与机会。 "}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-de7a76927406441c30a85914183814c8.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "84 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2057517515299878611"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI6sHDgYXj3JsdEAMaCTEyMDMyOTU2OSDi7K3SBjAAOBVAE3ITMjA1NzUxNzUxNTI5OTg3ODYxMXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1783653603.398623", "card_id": "Q_2058146846124552920", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 17}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "陈立泉、贲德获 2025 年度国家最高科学技术奖，他们取得了哪些成就？做出了哪些贡献？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "2025 年度国家最高科学技术奖 7 月 8 日在京揭晓，陈立泉院士、贲德院士获国家最高科学技术奖。 陈立泉，男，1940 年出生，中国科学院物理研究所研究员，我国锂电池领域的奠基人、开拓者和引领者，中国工程院院士。 贲德，男，1938 年出生，中国电子科技集团有限公司研究员，我国机载脉冲多普勒雷达技术的奠基者、相控阵雷达技术的主要开创者、天基监视雷达技术的先行者，中国工程院院士。 2025 年度国家科学技术奖共评选出 258 个项目和 11 名科技专家。其中，国家最高科学技术奖 2 人；国家自然科学奖 51 项，其中一等奖 3 项、二等奖 48 项；国家技术发明奖 58 项，其中一等奖 3 项、二等奖 55 项；国家科学技术进步奖 149 项，其中特等奖 3 项、一等奖 13 项、二等奖 133 项；授予 9 人中华人民共和国国际科学技术合作奖。 新华社权威快报 | 陈立泉、贲德获国家最高科学技术奖 "}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-83c57c9895781d4cf6385638ff9493a3_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "81 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2058146846124552920"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI6sHDgYXj3JsdEAMaCTEyMDM1Njg5MCD+gLfSBjAAOD1AFHITMjA1ODE0Njg0NjEyNDU1MjkyMHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1783653603.399871", "card_id": "Q_1936737896808841820", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 238}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "西游记里为什么唐僧只收孙悟空他们，不把红孩儿、黑熊怪等纳入取经队伍里去呢？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "或者说，为什么观音菩萨只收悟空、八戒、沙僧？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-6ac9c5f056540ce0ba134dce1346bcca.png"}, "metrics_